         <abstract>
            <p>The <foreign xml:lang="gez">ʾAnqaṣa bǝrhān</foreign> is a collection of hymns to be chanted on Sundays in praise of the 
            <persName ref="PRS6819Mary">Blessed Virgin</persName>.
            It is part of the Ethiopic <ref type="work" corresp="LIT2701Dawit">psalter</ref>, copied following the <ref type="work" corresp="LIT2509Weddas"/>. 
            Tradition ascribes its composition to <persName ref="PRS10245Yared" role="author">St Yāred</persName>.</p>
